repository.name: onnxruntime

issue.body:
Hello! I'm trying to build onnxruntime for android, I run it according to the tutorial https://onnxruntime.ai/docs/build/android.html, but i get error while build host_protoc:
* ::_wopen not found
* ::_waccess not found
* ::_wstat not found
* ::_wfopen not found
* std::once_flag not found
*  error: class 'google::protobuf::internal::CallOnceInitializedMutex<T>' does not have any field named 'flag_'
* call_once not found
* et cetera

it is similar #5008, but additional errors.

**System information**
- OS Platform and Distribution (e.g., Linux Ubuntu 16.04): Windows 11
- ONNX Runtime installed from (source or binary): source
- ONNX Runtime version: HEAD detached at v1.11.1
- Python version: Python 3.7.9
- Visual Studio version (if applicable): No
- GCC/Compiler version (if compiling from source): c++.exe (MinGW.org GCC-6.3.0-1) 6.3.0
- CUDA/cuDNN version: No
- GPU model and memory: No

**To Reproduce**
```bash
./build.bat --android --android_sdk_path <android_sdk_path >  --android_ndk_path <android_sdk_path >\ndk\24.0.8215888  --cmake_generator Ninja
```
